1
00:00:01,480 --> 00:00:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Hmm...</font>

2
00:00:03,860 --> 00:00:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All these houseplants 
just look the same to me.</font>

3
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Surely not.</font>

4
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cactus... I want a cactus!</font>

5
00:00:12,370 --> 00:00:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you complaining?</font>

6
00:00:15,070 --> 00:00:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who wanted some greenery 
in the classroom for summer, Nene.</font>

7
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whistle, whistle.</font>

8
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Yamabuki-kun.</font>

9
00:00:22,630 --> 00:00:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this one called?</font>

10
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a <i>Ficus benghalensis</i>.</font>

11
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Native to India's Bengal region, 
it's also known as a banyan.</font>

12
00:00:29,970 --> 00:00:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's known for being long-living.</font>

13
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's resilient and easy to raise, 
so it's perfect for beginners.</font>

14
00:00:35,250 --> 00:00:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But beware of the sap.</font>

15
00:00:35,250 --> 00:00:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Gross! He's a plant otaku!</font>

16
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It causes allergic reactions, 
so wear gloves when handling it.</font>

17
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus...</font>

18
00:00:38,270 --> 00:00:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus... Cactus... Cactus...</font>

19
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey.</font>

20
00:00:42,610 --> 00:00:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus!</font>

21
00:00:42,610 --> 00:00:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's pretty cute, no?</font>

22
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus...</font>

23
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a pachira.</font>

24
00:00:47,490 --> 00:00:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's known for its five-leaf stems 
and its rapid growth.</font>

25
00:00:48,210 --> 00:00:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus... Cactus...</font>

26
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus...</font>

27
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During spring and summer in particular, 
it'll grow a lot while you look away.</font>

28
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus! Cactus!</font>

29
00:00:57,710 --> 00:00:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cactus...</font>

30
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We came to this faraway store 
just to buy this one plant?</font>

31
00:01:04,630 --> 00:01:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We picked it because 
the five leaves represent us!</font>

32
00:01:08,990 --> 00:01:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More like because it was cheap, right?</font>

33
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted a cactus...</font>

34
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure is hot, though.</font>

35
00:01:14,860 --> 00:01:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Summer's almost here, after all.</font>

36
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I don't want to get sunburned.</font>

37
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I enjoyed the mini-concert the other day.</i></font>

38
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really do love singing my own songs.</i></font>

39
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to pull off a street 
performance the same way,</i></font>

40
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I'm too scared to try.</i></font>

41
00:01:37,330 --> 00:01:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Heck...</i></font>

42
00:01:38,370 --> 00:01:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still haven't managed to write a song.</i></font>

43
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do? Summer break's almost here.</i></font>

44
00:01:45,690 --> 00:01:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rikka still hasn't brought me a new song.</i></font>

45
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her trauma is deeper than I thought.</i></font>

46
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should probably explore other options. 
What can yours truly do?</i></font>

47
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty much anything, that's what!</font>

48
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?</font>

49
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that sound?</font>

50
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone's doing a street performance.</font>

51
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard this song before.</font>

52
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, go on without me!</font>

53
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

54
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on, Rikka-chan?</font>

55
00:02:18,350 --> 00:02:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bathroom break?</font>

56
00:02:19,570 --> 00:02:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm gonna be this tree's mommy?!</font>

57
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard that hypnosis 
can help one overcome trauma.</font>

58
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll ask my big sis to coach me.</font>

59
00:02:34,170 --> 00:02:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It really is Aiko. I could tell 
by the way she played.</i></font>

60
00:02:38,510 --> 00:02:41,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So she's still doing this, huh?</i></font>

61
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't be seen because it'd be awkward,</i></font>

62
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I want to stay and listen some more.</i></font>

63
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:51,480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Thank you.</i></font>

64
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The next song will be my last.</i></font>

65
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, missy.</font>

66
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody's even listening.</font>

67
00:02:57,750 --> 00:03:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the point in continuing?</font>

68
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh-oh...</i></font>

69
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:05,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shut your trap, moron!</i></font>

70
00:03:05,650 --> 00:03:07,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm doing this because I want to!</i></font>

71
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what? 
You're shit at this, so just quit!</font>

72
00:03:11,510 --> 00:03:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you've got shit for ears, asshole!</font>

73
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not gonna put up with 
anyone who insults my music!</font>

74
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're never gonna make it anywhere! Pah!</font>

75
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Shut it, fool!</i></font>

76
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:22,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Never show me your face again, 
you old fart!</i></font>

77
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:26,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Anyway, here's my last song.</i></font>

78
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:29,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I didn't write this song by myself.</i></font>

79
00:03:29,890 --> 00:03:32,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I wrote it with a friend of mine 
a long time ago.</i></font>

80
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:36,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>We did music together 
back in middle school.</i></font>

81
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:38,940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>We were so excited 
when we finished the song,</i></font>

82
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:42,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>thinking we made a masterpiece, 
and we sent it to a record label.</i></font>

83
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:44,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>We actually got a response, too.</i></font>

84
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one of you sang the chorus?</font>

85
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only need the girl with that voice.</font>

86
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But I was still happy,</i></font>

87
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:56,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>because our music had been acknowledged.</i></font>

88
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:59,780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's why I entrusted 
everything to my friend.</i></font>

89
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:02,050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I told her she'd better make it!</i></font>

90
00:04:02,050 --> 00:04:05,300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She'd better become the number one 
artist in Japan with our music!</i></font>

91
00:04:06,530 --> 00:04:09,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But what did that idiot do?</i></font>

92
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:12,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She had a setback or two 
and ran away from the record label!</i></font>

93
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:17,160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Quit chickening out and running 
to covers of idol songs, you moron!</i></font>

94
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:21,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What kind of middle-schooler brat 
gives up after one failure?!</i></font>

95
00:04:23,690 --> 00:04:27,750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So I have to keep singing this song.</i></font>

96
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:30,500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>After all, her talent is the real deal.</i></font>

97
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:34,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even if she wasn't 
Japan's number one artist,</i></font>

98
00:04:34,010 --> 00:04:37,210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>she could still be number one 
in someone's heart.</i></font>

99
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:41,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So it's fine as long 
as somebody understands.</i></font>

100
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:44,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If you come to like this song, 
please remember it.</i></font>

101
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"The Calm of Night."</i></font>

102
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As the sun sank into the sea</i></font>

103
00:05:06,690 --> 00:05:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We let out a deep sigh</i></font>

104
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the oceans responded to us</i></font>

105
00:05:12,910 --> 00:05:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a big white wave</i></font>

106
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And dragged the wind away with it</i></font>

107
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep watching this 5-yen coin, 
and what do you know...</font>

108
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll find that even a lemon 
can taste sweet like sugar</font>

109
00:05:30,790 --> 00:05:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, I'm starting to believe!</font>

110
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, go ahead and eat that lemon slice.</font>

111
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sour!</font>

112
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Breathe in... breathe out.</font>

113
00:05:43,570 --> 00:05:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My tongue...</font>

114
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It didn't work at all.</font>

115
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping to remove 
Rikka's trauma this way!</font>

116
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka's starting her mini-concert.</font>

117
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while since her last one!</font>

118
00:05:57,290 --> 00:05:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, everyone.</font>

119
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for coming 
even though it's so hot.</font>

120
00:06:02,850 --> 00:06:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get right to it. 
Here's the first song.</font>

121
00:06:05,650 --> 00:06:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what's the title?</font>

122
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wonder what she's gonna perform.</font>

123
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As the sun sank into the sea</i></font>

124
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that song?</font>

125
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is it an original?</font>

126
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We let out a deep sigh</i></font>

127
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the oceans responded to us</i></font>

128
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this song?</font>

129
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a big white wave</i></font>

130
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, I wanted the usual stuff.</font>

131
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And dragged the wind away with it</i></font>

132
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This doesn't feel like her.</font>

133
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know, I think I like this better.</font>

134
00:06:45,090 --> 00:06:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}After we saw it off</i></font>

135
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We made a promise for no reason</i></font>

136
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Yeah...</i></font>

137
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The calm takes over the night</i></font>

138
00:06:58,540 --> 00:07:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When the calm takes over the night</i></font>

139
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:08,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We feel like there's nobody else 
in the world but us</i></font>

140
00:07:08,490 --> 00:07:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The sea blends into the sky</i></font>

141
00:07:11,730 --> 00:07:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When the sea quietly blends into the sky</i></font>

142
00:07:15,550 --> 00:07:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I know it's just the two of us</i></font>

143
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But I still whisper to you</i></font>

144
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When did she write a song like this?</i></font>

145
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Ah, in the calm of night</i></font>

146
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's more, she did it all on her own, 
without yours truly's help?</i></font>

147
00:07:34,890 --> 00:07:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka!</font>

148
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you write that original song?</font>

149
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:41,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really good!</font>

150
00:07:41,230 --> 00:07:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems I've underestimated you!</font>

151
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've grown a lot when I wasn't looking!</font>

152
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously.</font>

153
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't given me 
enough attention lately.</font>

154
00:07:52,470 --> 00:07:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

155
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For this song, I stopped caring 
about appealing to everyone.</font>

156
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wrote it for someone special to me—</font>

157
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my best friend,</font>

158
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and one more throw-in.</font>

159
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a throw-in, huh?</font>

160
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WHILE YOU LOOK AWAY</font>

161
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have a date and time 
for the street performance!</font>

162
00:09:47,070 --> 00:09:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've secured a venue, too. 
Now we just need your songs.</font>

163
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, rock my inner ear 
with the power of your new songs!</font>

164
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

165
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka's working on a song right now.</font>

166
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad.</font>

167
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Bucky, your regular voice 
is already loud enough.</font>

168
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you say you were done?</font>

169
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still one left.</font>

170
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm planning to put five songs on the CD 
I'm selling at the performance.</font>

171
00:10:10,850 --> 00:10:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I just can't finish the last song.</font>

172
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Considering how you couldn't write 
at all before, this is good progress.</font>

173
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're doing well.</font>

174
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Don't throw 
my praise out the window!</font>

175
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka ain't an easy lass.</font>

176
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I finished the draft for my CD cover.</font>

177
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show us! Show us!</font>

178
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

179
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you hate rabbits?</font>

180
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a peace sign, not a rabbit.</font>

181
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what does this mean?</font>

182
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

183
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a symbol for defiance.</font>

184
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure it spreads 
to all corners of Japan.</font>

185
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

186
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. Now even I'm starting to get nervous.</font>

187
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll all come watch your show, okay?</font>

188
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, about that...</font>

189
00:10:57,330 --> 00:10:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For this show,</font>

190
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to do it without your help.</font>

191
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

192
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having you there would make me 
happy and help me relax,</font>

193
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if I got too used to that, 
there'd be no point to this show.</font>

194
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

195
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a shame, but I guess 
it's for your own good.</font>

196
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, gotcha.</font>

197
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we'll be at the next show, okay?</font>

198
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way...</font>

199
00:11:21,370 --> 00:11:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd you suddenly make progress 
after being stuck for so long?</font>

200
00:11:24,570 --> 00:11:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you find a song-writing trick
 or something?</font>

201
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trick? Hmm...</font>

202
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this time, I'd been trying to write 
songs that'd appeal to lots of people.</font>

203
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Songs I wouldn't be ashamed of, 
songs that would actually sell.</font>

204
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I was trying to do, 
but it just didn't go well.</font>

205
00:11:40,350 --> 00:11:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I tried writing them while picturing 
the person I'm dedicating them to,</font>

206
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the lyrics and melodies 
came naturally to me.</font>

207
00:11:48,470 --> 00:11:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, I wasn't making 
music to send some kind of message.</font>

208
00:11:52,860 --> 00:11:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was making music because I wanted 
this person to listen to my songs.</font>

209
00:11:57,740 --> 00:12:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my pen stopped moving 
while writing this last song.</font>

210
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

211
00:12:05,290 --> 00:12:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I want to say something,</font>

212
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">maybe I should tell them directly 
instead of using my music.</font>

213
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. She's reached an impasse.</i></font>

214
00:12:15,650 --> 00:12:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As a producer, I should resolve this 
and have her write the best song ever.</i></font>

215
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

216
00:12:23,490 --> 00:12:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything I can do for you?</font>

217
00:12:25,770 --> 00:12:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can get you anything you desire, 
be it a place, a situation, or people.</font>

218
00:12:29,490 --> 00:12:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, you sound like a scrub 
who got rich.</font>

219
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything? Really?</font>

220
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! For yours truly, 
impossible is nothing!</font>

221
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

222
00:12:44,950 --> 00:12:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamabuki-kun, over here.</font>

223
00:12:47,370 --> 00:12:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did say I could get you anything...</font>

224
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why ask to chat with me 
by the beach at night?</font>

225
00:12:53,650 --> 00:12:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to write songs 
at midnight just like this.</font>

226
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought being here might help.</font>

227
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a little chat with me.</font>

228
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come sit next to me.</font>

229
00:13:17,420 --> 00:13:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About what you said earlier today...</font>

230
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Making music for just one person." 
That's a good way to go about it.</font>

231
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, Beethoven supposedly 
dedicated "Für Elise" to someone he loved,</font>

232
00:13:29,340 --> 00:13:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it's still beloved 
200 years later.</font>

233
00:13:31,930 --> 00:13:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's amazing that you discovered 
this method all on your own.</font>

234
00:13:35,310 --> 00:13:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great job, Rikka.</font>

235
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

236
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you dedicating those songs to?</font>

237
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I'm too embarrassed to say.</font>

238
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just say it's someone I once 
distanced myself from out of awkwardness,</font>

239
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now I need to work up the courage 
to tell them how I feel, maybe?</font>

240
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

241
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She must be talking about 
her friend, that Aiko girl.</i></font>

242
00:13:56,730 --> 00:13:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They did have a falling out 
over musical styles.</i></font>

243
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And?</font>

244
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to tell 
this person through your music?</font>

245
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to tell you here?</font>

246
00:14:07,290 --> 00:14:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't know unless you tell me.</font>

247
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I love you."</font>

248
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's rather direct, but she wants 
to convey her love for her friend, huh?</i></font>

249
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?</font>

250
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

251
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Rikka. 
Can I take a look at your lyrics?</font>

252
00:14:28,460 --> 00:14:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

253
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or I won't know anything.</font>

254
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but...</font>

255
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's getting embarrassed going to help?</font>

256
00:14:37,770 --> 00:14:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

257
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

258
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

259
00:14:42,130 --> 00:14:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, are you being evasive on purpose?</font>

260
00:14:45,530 --> 00:14:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These lyrics are pretty abstract 
and avoid expressing anything directly.</font>

261
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They won't get the message. 
What exactly do you love about them?</font>

262
00:14:53,930 --> 00:14:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

263
00:14:54,850 --> 00:14:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er...</font>

264
00:14:57,270 --> 00:15:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, uh... they were a good listener 
to me late at night...</font>

265
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and encouraged me to pursue my dream.</font>

266
00:15:05,060 --> 00:15:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really enjoyed talking to them, 
and they gave me hope.</font>

267
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else? Give me more.</font>

268
00:15:12,060 --> 00:15:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Urk...</font>

269
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-They're kind...</font>

270
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, and?</font>

271
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have a pleasant voice.</font>

272
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep going!</font>

273
00:15:20,930 --> 00:15:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the biggest thing...</font>

274
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is that they waited for me all this time 
after I ran away from them.</font>

275
00:15:26,490 --> 00:15:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a thoughtful person!</font>

276
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? You've got all these things to say.</font>

277
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not use your lyrics to do it?</font>

278
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like cheating to use music 
to express what I couldn't say directly.</font>

279
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I express my feelings that way, 
it might disappoint them.</font>

280
00:15:44,300 --> 00:15:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like they'd want to hear what 
they really want to hear directly from me.</font>

281
00:15:49,820 --> 00:15:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

282
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

283
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

284
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little Miss Want-It-All!</font>

285
00:15:54,090 --> 00:15:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

286
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are blessed with a gift!</font>

287
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can express yourself 
in a way most people can't!</font>

288
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's there to debate?!</font>

289
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no hierarchy in self-expression!</font>

290
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not the method—it's the strength 
of feeling that moves the heart.</font>

291
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not using a gift you have goes against 
the Yamabukis' way of life!</font>

292
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm an Inohana, though? Let's say...</font>

293
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's say someone used a song 
to express their feelings to you.</font>

294
00:16:17,930 --> 00:16:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you be happy?</font>

295
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

296
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very happy.</font>

297
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

298
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I guess I'll leave 
this song off the CD.</font>

299
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I thought I just 
got rid of your worries!</font>

300
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because this last song is meant 
to express something very dear to me.</font>

301
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once I can call myself an artist—</font>

302
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">once I feel I have the right to use 
music as a means of expression—</font>

303
00:16:52,210 --> 00:16:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">only then will I release it to the world.</font>

304
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to save it 
for a Budokan concert?</font>

305
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing that grand.</font>

306
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this street performance goes well</font>

307
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I manage to sell 50 copies of my CD,</font>

308
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then...</font>

309
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll sing it to the person dear to me.</font>

310
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm performing here?</font>

311
00:17:22,130 --> 00:17:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed. This park is known as 
a mecca for street performances.</font>

312
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Celestial, the latest-and-hottest 
band right now,</font>

313
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">performed here 
until last year too, I hear.</font>

314
00:17:32,630 --> 00:17:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the audience will have 
pretty high standards.</font>

315
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you can pick up fans here, 
you'll surely make a name for yourself.</font>

316
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made fliers and distributed them.</font>

317
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to make a good first 
impression to win the audience over.</font>

318
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I secured you a spot with 
plenty of space and visibility.</font>

319
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm getting a sharp pain in my chest.</i></font>

320
00:17:55,840 --> 00:18:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This brings back memories. 
I was nervous the first time, too.</i></font>

321
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

322
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a different kind of pain now.</i></font>

323
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, I knew nothing 
and was full of wide-eyed hope,</i></font>

324
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but now I'm just scared.</i></font>

325
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Scared they'll look at me 
with those eyes again.</i></font>

326
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What now?</i></font>

327
00:18:14,630 --> 00:18:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I probably can't do this.</i></font>

328
00:18:16,370 --> 00:18:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I should just call it off, 
or something...</i></font>

329
00:18:19,410 --> 00:18:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

330
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

331
00:18:21,930 --> 00:18:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you find my eyes scary?</font>

332
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Not really?</font>

333
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:27,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? Aren't they lovely?</font>

334
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't put words in my mouth.</font>

335
00:18:30,260 --> 00:18:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Rikka.</font>

336
00:18:31,490 --> 00:18:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're having a hard time during 
the show and can't keep your head up,</font>

337
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just look into my eyes.</font>

338
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

339
00:18:39,130 --> 00:18:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great.</font>

340
00:18:40,210 --> 00:18:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a good thing I came prepared.</font>

341
00:18:43,370 --> 00:18:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you lose sight of me 
among a sea of spectators,</font>

342
00:18:46,540 --> 00:18:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll be able to see me wave these!</font>

343
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd die of cringe, so don't you dare.</font>

344
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You'd use the word "cringe" 
to describe yours truly?!</font>

345
00:18:57,150 --> 00:19:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're helping me loosen up, huh? Thanks.</font>

346
00:19:00,300 --> 00:19:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give it a shot.</font>

347
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, do your best.</font>

348
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll watch over you the whole time.</font>

349
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}500 YEN PER CD</font>

350
00:19:16,050 --> 00:19:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}INOHANA RIKKA</font>

351
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go with my first song, 
"Flickering Days."</font>

352
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As we looked up the open blue sky</i></font>

353
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you... wanna do now?</font>

354
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In bright white letters</i></font>

355
00:19:49,650 --> 00:19:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We wrote about our purpose, 
we wrote about our future</i></font>

356
00:19:54,050 --> 00:19:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And painted it with our dreams</i></font>

357
00:19:57,950 --> 00:20:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With each passing "See you tomorrow"</i></font>

358
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her voice lacks its usual oomph, 
and she's not in the right rhythm.</i></font>

359
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I suppose it's not that easy
 to get rid of her anxiety.</i></font>

360
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our hearts grew closer</i></font>

361
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As we have good times and bad</i></font>

362
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With no audience, her 
mental state will only worsen.</i></font>

363
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We walk in awkward strides</i></font>

364
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You need to stay calm, Rikka.</i></font>

365
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We hold hands tight, 
and our words reach each other</i></font>

366
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it wouldn't work.</i></font>

367
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody's stopping.</i></font>

368
00:20:20,510 --> 00:20:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And gently push us forward</i></font>

369
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody's listening to my song.</i></font>

370
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The round postbox, the usual crosswalk</i></font>

371
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought you'd be up for it.</i></font>

372
00:20:26,380 --> 00:20:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That teary face, the shining smile</i></font>

373
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}They're all de—</i></font>

374
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I expected too much of you.</i></font>

375
00:20:35,630 --> 00:20:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Aiko. I just can't...</font>

376
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

377
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Huh? We got lost and wound up here...</font>

378
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your acting's way too awkward!</font>

379
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Come on! 
We don't want to miss our train!</font>

380
00:20:56,110 --> 00:21:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine we're always in the front row.</font>

381
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right, I'd forgotten.</i></font>

382
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw trying to sing for lots of people.</i></font>

383
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll just sing for the people 
I want to hear my song.</i></font>

384
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:16,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Here's my second song, 
"ask for the moon."</i></font>

385
00:21:26,950 --> 00:21:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wrote this song for my three 
fellow broadcasting club members.</i></font>

386
00:21:31,630 --> 00:21:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So they're the only people 
I need to sing for.</i></font>

387
00:21:36,610 --> 00:21:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I believe these hands, my voice</i></font>

388
00:21:41,130 --> 00:21:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will get to where I want them to go</i></font>

389
00:21:53,690 --> 00:21:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}380,000 kilometers</i></font>

390
00:21:57,140 --> 00:22:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}From an impossible distance</i></font>

391
00:21:59,130 --> 00:22:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I made the right call by asking 
for their help.</i></font>

392
00:22:02,150 --> 00:22:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BROADCASTING ROOM (TEMP)</font>

393
00:22:02,870 --> 00:22:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You steal my heart away</i></font>

394
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? She's lying?</font>

395
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And shine a light on my solitude</i></font>

396
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. She said not to come because she 
didn't want to be overly reliant on you,</font>

397
00:22:11,020 --> 00:22:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Whether it was coincidence 
or a magic spell</i></font>

398
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's not all.</font>

399
00:22:13,330 --> 00:22:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She doesn't want you to see her fail.</font>

400
00:22:15,740 --> 00:22:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The clouds give way to a ray of hope</i></font>

401
00:22:16,380 --> 00:22:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's scared that you might look at her 
with disappointment in your eyes.</font>

402
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd never look at her 
that way, you dumbass!</font>

403
00:22:21,310 --> 00:22:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Is it possible or impossible</i></font>

404
00:22:23,020 --> 00:22:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, never!</font>

405
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will it come true or not</i></font>

406
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why get mad at me?</font>

407
00:22:25,210 --> 00:22:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What can we do, then?</font>

408
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Nobody knows</i></font>

409
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to watch her show up close.</font>

410
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That's why I hope, that's why I journey</i></font>

411
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just be there for Rikka.</font>

412
00:22:34,310 --> 00:22:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Using my dreams as footholds</i></font>

413
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's getting better and better.</i></font>

414
00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keep it up and reel them in!</i></font>

415
00:22:41,850 --> 00:22:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know your voice can reach them, Rikka!</i></font>

416
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Wanting to touch the waxing 
and waning moon</i></font>

417
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I reached out</i></font>

418
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if it was a small, 
insignificant step</i></font>

419
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I traveled my universe</i></font>

420
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Believing I'll get there someday</i></font>

421
00:23:06,410 --> 00:23:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That girl has a lovely voice.</font>

422
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if I must walk down 
a path never trodden before</i></font>

423
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to stay and listen?</font>

424
00:23:13,290 --> 00:23:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if I'm dreaming too big, 
hoping for too much</i></font>

425
00:23:17,810 --> 00:23:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My hand traverses 
a 60-centimeter universe</i></font>

426
00:23:22,620 --> 00:23:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And gets closer to 
the bright side of the moon</i></font>

427
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Watch me</i></font>

428
00:23:35,990 --> 00:23:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}See?</i></font>

429
00:23:36,980 --> 00:23:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: SRIRAM GURUNATHAN
TIMING: MARIANA MARTINEZ
EDITING: WILLIAM HAGGARD</font>

430
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CHECK: S BILYEU
TRANSLATION CHECK: MICHELLE TYMON</font>

